title: The Seafarers - The Spanish Main - Peter Wood.epub
description:
EPUB. The Ruthless Conquest of a Golden Aztec Empire, The First Challenges to the Lords of the Main, Carrying the King's Wealth to the Coffers of Seville, The Merchant who Enflamed Spain's New World, The Fire and Fury of El Dragon, The Heretics Who Humbled the Might of Spain, The Rise of a Bloodthirsty Brotherhood, A Sea-Roving Devil Named Henry Morgan, The Sacking of Cartagena - A Last Bold Stroke, Essay: A New Era of Naval Warfare on the Embattled Main.
There is no Bibliography, Acknowledgements, Picture Credits or Index. A lot of pictures were spread across two pages, they are not included, other pictures have been moved to the end of the chapter they were in.
